    If the flag can be enabled/disabled, then it should implement this to help other plugins to understand your flag

    If the flag has a group key override, then it should implement this to assist other plugins attempting to understand

    Flag.ValueStore
     
    FlagType<F extends Flag>
    A flag type is the specific type of a flag, each flag should have a unique FlagType which is designed to serialize and deserialize the flag as well as provide generic metadata about the flag itself
